---
title: Mushroom & Lentil Shepherd's Pie with Cheesy Mash Topping & Garlicky Greens
description: Homey, comforting classics like this shepherd’s pie nourish us from the inside out. We’re combining the soft textures of mushrooms with a hearty lentil filling, covered in a cheesy mash to create the most heartwarming meal for tonight’s dinner.
